really think of Graham.

817
00:46:30,822 --> 00:46:31,954
In all honesty?

818
00:46:31,956 --> 00:46:33,556
Yeah.

819
00:46:33,558 --> 00:46:36,492
He's good.

820
00:46:36,494 --> 00:46:38,194
Good?

821
