00:47:55,573 --> 00:47:58,274
Not just because of the
whole "Tami/Tommy" thing either,

847
00:47:58,276 --> 00:47:59,876
even though that was
really fun.

848
00:47:59,878 --> 00:48:02,211
Um, but no, we had the same
tastes in

