00:48:05,583 --> 00:48:07,583
We're both really
into shoes big-time.

851
00:48:07,585 --> 00:48:09,185
We both loved
the same shows.

852
00:48:09,187 --> 00:48:10,620
That was
important to me.

853
00:48:10,622 --> 00:48:12,655
