986
00:54:17,588 --> 00:54:20,289
Huh.
Oh, no.

987
00:54:20,291 --> 00:54:21,624
BOTH:
It's Grandma's boyfriend.

988
00:54:21,626 --> 00:54:23,359
(both chuckle)

989
00:54:23,361 --> 00:54:24,526
