1025
00:55:44,775 --> 00:55:46,842
Get you two artistes
a couple of brews?

1026
00:55:46,844 --> 00:55:48,010
Sure. Two darks.

1027
00:55:48,012 --> 00:55:49,678
I'd rather get...
Ay, yi...

